With a variety of ailments it can treat, aloe vera is a popular choice for those seeking natural remedies for colds and flu.

The Eiffel Tower is a famous landmark in Paris, France. It was built in 1889 to commemorate the centenary of the French Revolution, and stands 324 meters tall on the Champ de Mars. The wrought iron lattice tower is a symbol of France and is visited by millions of people from around the world each year. It is often painted in the colors of the French flag - blue, white, and red - and lit up at night to create a beautiful and magical atmosphere. The Eiffel Tower is a popular destination for romantic walks and taking photos, and it is surrounded by water from the nearby river.
